    "notes": [
      "Using README-provided training commands verbatim, with explicit -name added where missing for deterministic artifact discovery.",
      "Skipped install_deps task because execution environment is docker paper_image; avoid redundant runtime installs unless image is missing dependencies.",
      "Added dataset extraction via preprocess.sh as local preparation step because repository includes compressed data and README/setup mentions extraction.",
      "No separate evaluator task added: no README-documented checkpoint evaluation/export command provided, and local eval script usage is unspecified."
    ]
